item.title: Israel Kamakawiwo'ole - What A Wonderful World - Key of C
item.description: Play along video for the song What A Wonderful World performed by Israel Kamakawiwo'ole. Chords used in the song: Am, Am7, C, Dm7, E7, Em, F, G.
